casebody.data:
GREAT LAKES EYE INSTITUTE, P.C., Plaintiff/Counterdefendant-Appellant,
v.
David B. KREBS, M.D., Defendant/Counterplaintiff-Appellee. SC: 157526
COA: 335405 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 4, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for miscellaneous relief is GRANTED. The application for leave to appeal the January 9, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should now be reviewed by this Court.
